text: Hasan Kaya (born 10 November 1995) is a German footballer who plays as a forward for Turkish club Nevşehir Belediyespor on loan from Ankaragücü. ==Professional career== Kaya made his professional debut Ankaragücü with in a 1-1 Süper Lig tie with Kayserispor on 24 August 2019. ==References == ==External links== * * Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Sportspeople from Hamburg Category:German footballers Category:German people of Turkish descent Category:Association football forwards Category:Süper Lig players Category:TFF Second League players Category:MKE Ankaragücü footballers
